data.description: THE WAIT IS OVER!!!  Are you looking for the ideal home without the long wait of a new construction? This Beautiful 4 bedroom, 3 bath is your ideal home.  As you enter through the large glass door, you are greeted with a formal Living Room with beautiful tile flooring, which continues throughout the home. The lovely kitchen has black STAINLESS STEEL appliances, 42in CABINETS and GRANITE counter tops. The dining area flows seamlessly into the spacious living room, creating an open and inviting atmosphere.  The owner's suite is separated from the other 3 bedrooms, giving you the privacy you are looking for. The owner's bathroom has a separate jetted tub that you will appreciate after a long, busy day. The 2nd Bedroom also has an ensuite bathroom. Features include cordless blinds, granite countertops and ceiling fans throughout.  The bonus room that can be used for so many options such as a game room, theatre room or even a man cave, the sky is the limit. The French doors leading to the patio are equipped with built in blinds, which give a luxury feel with no hanging strings. This property has a huge backyard where you can create your own personal oasis that will be great for large gatherings or even add on a mother-in-law suite. This beautiful Sarasota home is move-in ready, with all the features and amenities you need to start enjoying your new lifestyle right away. In addition to the luxurious upgrades already mentioned, this home is only a year old. This means you can rest assured that you'll have a comfortable home with reliable cooling and protection from the elements for years to come. With no need to worry about major repairs or upgrades, you can focus on enjoying your new home and all the amazing features it has to offer. No HOA, no deed restrictions and no CDD fees, giving you the freedom to truly make it your own. So, bring your RV, boat, or any other recreational vehicle for true sunshine state living.  With a huge backyard and shed, surrounded by a privacy fence. Take a look at this SPECTACULAR property in close proximity to Sarasota hotspots. Only two miles to Downtown Sarasota, close to Siesta key Beach, Lido Beach and too many other wonderful spots. So why wait? Don't miss your chance to own this stunning Sarasota home - schedule your visit today and get ready to start living the Florida dream!
